law.history: Repealed 1946Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 35, effective January 1, 1947. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2739n-9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Judgment to be satisfied and proof of ability to pay damages to be filed before future licensing or registration; nonresidents.
